NAME
    Perinci::Util - Utility routines

VERSION
    version 0.27

DESCRIPTION
    This is a temporary module containing utility routines.

    It should be split once it's rather big.

FUNCTIONS
  declare_property
  declare_function_dep
  declare_function_feature
  get_package_meta_accessor(%args)
    Arguments: "package", "default_class" (optional, defaults to
    "Perinci::MetaAccessor::Default").

